{
  "title": "Working with Audio",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Working with Audio</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\"> Explore Unreal Engine's audio tools. </p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Working with Audio\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/d3b26e84-946f-4247-bb0a-ba84fef5535f?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/d3b26e84-946f-4247-bb0a-ba84fef5535f?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/d3b26e84-946f-4247-bb0a-ba84fef5535f?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"12\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"11\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Sound is vital to creating believable and immersive environments. From ambient sounds to interactive sounds of vehicles or weapons, from music cues to spoken dialog, audio in a game can make or break the user experience.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">The Audio Engine system in Unreal Engine provides tools and features that offer ways for audio designers and engineers to mold audio to match their visions. This means that a clean version of the sound can be produced once in an external application, imported, then crafted within the engine to create the desired result.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 id=\"topics\" data-previous-ids=\"topics\"> Topics </h2><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><ul block-document-list=\"\" class=\"block-document-list\" ngh=\"10\"><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:audio-analysis-and-visualization-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/4a6b62ad-3184-446b-9dea-920e53f874c6?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Audio Analysis and Visualization\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Audio Analysis and Visualization</p><p class=\"description\">A collection of topics related to audio analysis and visualization in Unreal Engine.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:audio-debugging-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/3636602a-9880-481e-9ad0-868af4dffa8a?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Audio Debugging\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Audio Debugging</p><p class=\"description\">A collection of topics related to audio debugging in Unreal Engine.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:audio-gameplay-volumes-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e1dc8c61-8eb5-485d-af35-6193b4d5c29b?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Audio Gameplay Volumes\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Audio Gameplay Volumes</p><p class=\"description\">A collection of topics related to Audio Gameplay Volumes in Unreal Engine.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:audio-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/3bbeb701-0344-44f0-b4d3-4a74ef497b92?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Audio in Unreal Engine\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Audio in Unreal Engine</p><p class=\"description\">A collection of topics related to audio in Unreal Engine.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item